### Mermaid overview

```
flowchart TB
    laptop["💻 Laptop (kubectl)"]
    inet1((Internet))
    api["AKS API Server<br/>(Azure managed control plane)<br/>Free tier — no node"]

    subgraph snet["snet-aks (10.10.1.0/24)"]
        node["AKS Node<br/>Standard_D2s_v3 (2 vCPU)"]
        ksys["kube-system pods"]
        upods["user pods (nginx demo)"]
        node --- ksys
        node --- upods
    end

    acr["ACR (Basic SKU)<br/>AKS auth via ACR role"]

    laptop -->|"HTTPS :443<br/>allowlist IP"| inet1
    inet1 --> api
    api -->|"kubelet, image pull"| node
    node -->|"image pull via<br/>managed identity"| acr

    inet2((Internet))
    slb["Standard Load Balancer<br/>(auto create by Service type=LoadBalancer)"]
    pnginx["Pod nginx (cluster IP)"]

    inet2 --> slb
    slb --> pnginx

```